OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776175862
OL,3,CSouthport report finds failures by
OL,4,Cauthorities - and at home
OL,6,FThe words "failure", "failing" and
OL,7,F"failed" appear more than 200 times in
OL,8,FMonday's Southport report.
OL,10,FIts findings leave almost no agency,
OL,11,Forganisation or individual involved in
OL,12,FAxel Rudakubana's life unscathed.
OL,14,FThe police, council, mental health
OL,15,Fservices, Prevent programme ` none of
OL,16,Fthem took ownership of the risks that
OL,17,Fhe posed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
