OL,3,CSouthport report finds failures by
OL,4,Cauthorities - and at home
OL,6,FOnly The Acorn School, which the
OL,7,Fattacker attended after being expelled
OL,8,Ffrom Range High School, is noted as
OL,9,Fhaving repeatedly intervened.
OL,11,FBut the Chair of the inquiry, Sir
OL,12,FAdrian Fulford, also clearly believes
OL,13,Fin parental responsibility.
OL,15,FThe attacker's father, in particular,
OL,16,Fis described as "obstructive" and
OL,17,F"manipulative" in relation to the
OL,18,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
