OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776175862
OL,3,CSouthport report finds failures by
OL,4,Cauthorities - and at home
OL,6,FIt is rare to see a killer's parents
OL,7,Fsingled-out for not doing more to
OL,8,Fprevent their child's crimes.
OL,10,FTogether, the Southport attack was a
OL,11,Ffailure of both parenting and policy `
OL,12,Fnobody, says the Chair, agreed who was
OL,13,Fresponsible for the troubled teenager.
OL,15,FThere was a "merry-go-round of
OL,16,Freferrals, assessments, case-closures
OL,17,Fand 'hand-offs'", he says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
