OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776175862
OL,3,CSouthport report finds failures by
OL,4,Cauthorities - and at home
OL,6,FThere is even a specific moment when
OL,7,FSir Adrian believes the murders could
OL,8,Fhave been prevented, after the
OL,9,Fattacker was caught with a knife on a
OL,10,Fbus in 2022.
OL,12,FBut no arrest or search of his home
OL,13,Ftook place, leaving the poison in his
OL,14,Fbedroom and the warped search history
OL,15,Fon his computer undetected.
OL,17,FThe report's recommendations include
OL,18,Fsetting up an agency with overall
OL,19,Fresponsibility for monitoring risk, to
OL,20,Favoid repeat failings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
